{"tid":1156680,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我前世係咪做二五背叛哂所有朋友","createTime":"2019-05-15T18:27:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-15T18:53:10.000Z","uid":154093,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9554a15f94d471e8fd20f7579ddec76bc6ca0357","tid":1156680,"uid":154093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T18:27:00.000Z","msg":"所以依家先得翻班撚屌fd<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中學嗰陣大部分都日日見以為自己真係好多fd<br />\n畢業之後先發現原來真係firm到嘅fd冇乜幾個<br />\n<br />\n新識嘅<br />\n全部hi bye（大家聚埋一齊嘅原因只會係因為嗰段時間冇人陪）<br />\n舊嘅<br />\n一係就各有各忙 有緣再聚 其實大家各行各路好正常<br />\n仲keep住約到 得閒聚下已經好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一係就有一堆人 口口聲聲就話兄弟best fd 佢哋會約出嚟 但唔會叫埋你 你可以一齊嚟㗎 不過你唔嚟 一切都會照常 （有時真係懷疑佢哋有冇當過我係fd）<br />\n<br />\n真係冇諗過自己號召力咁撚低 得翻一個兄弟真係叫firm<br />\n想打場5排LOL都做唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nPS所以真係要識翻個女朋友 有咩心事負能量都可以有人分擔下 所謂朋友真係靠唔撚住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24e15a335823c16116700e89dfb4ab5b6986ab9c","tid":1156680,"uid":201604,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T18:29:03.000Z","msg":"真 朋友冇撚用 另一半先係最重要"},{"pid":"0eb0afe8b7f4ad1e20aceb4d218d6a1f56502882","tid":1156680,"uid":154093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"24e15a335823c16116700e89dfb4ab5b6986ab9c","tid":1156680,"uid":201604,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T18:29:03.000Z","msg":"真 朋友冇撚用 另一半先係最重要"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T18:48:11.000Z","msg":"朋友只係一種假象"},{"pid":"02e07a071570dda1a188185a7453efcc6b6b4844","tid":1156680,"uid":240150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T18:49:17.000Z","msg":"女朋友都會走"},{"pid":"794457b199e1661b646bf2d34874bff9e6b1b240","tid":1156680,"uid":154093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"02e07a071570dda1a188185a7453efcc6b6b4844","tid":1156680,"uid":240150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTim